I love this quote for many reasons, hello #lawofattraction #manifestation, but also just because it’s very true. think about a time when you had a desire, a dream, a goal, and it literally felt impossible. oh that job? impossible. that car, that relationship, that life? now fast forward however much time, and remember when it actually happened. regardless how it got there (that manifestation talk is for an upcoming *virtual wellness retreat*), here is your thing that you wanted but thought would never come.

ya’ll humans are amazing. we are insane, life is insane. we are literally capable of doing some incredible and dare I say ~impossible~ stuff. so stop psyching yourself out. stop saying no to things you want but are too scared or inpatient. you never know what you can actually achieve until you try. so go do all the things!!! they’re closer than you think. 🌈";}i:173;a:1:{s:14:"comments_count";i:1;}i:174;a:1:{s:11:"likes_count";i:8;}i:175;a:1:{s:4:"link";s:39:"https://www.instagram.com/p/CEu3JqFjQHJ";}i:176;a:1:{s:5:"image";s:249:"https://scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/p1080x1080/118738424_668110530473536_5061746609209360977_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=104&_nc_ohc=oAyDhd5kFQMAX-F9lU1&oh=ff69d5af32e673a2aafb02840fb77078&oe=5F7CAA32";}i:177;a:1:{s:4:"type";s:5:"image";}i:178;a:1:{s:8:"owner_id";i:28609734185;}i:179;a:1:{s:14:"owner_username";s:0:"";}i:180;a:1:{s:14:"owner_fullname";s:0:"";}i:181;a:1:{s:9:"owner_pic";s:0:"";}i:182;a:1:{s:2:"id";s:19:"2391090020939039775";}i:183;a:1:{s:10:"short_code";s:11:"CEu27ScDYQf";}i:184;a:1:{s:12:"created_time";i:1599260164;}i:185;a:1:{s:7:"caption";s:1741:"Grounded AF #getgrounded
