Day 2 - open to new projects (any heart opener)

I’m open to every new opportunity this year. And till now had no regrets. For example, at the end of this month I’ll officially be a certified yoga teacher and I took this decision from nowhere. I wanted to learn more about yoga, more than just the awesome asanas I learned in this pandemic, and more about pranayama practices and meditation. I felt the need to explore that part. To know myself better. To love myself(better). 🙏🏻 

